	$220880: 'Space yourselves out along the road.',
	$220890: 'Use that wire to set up an obstacle across the road.',
	$220900: 'Block that road with the barbed wire!',
	$220910: 'Here they come!',
	$220920: "Let's go!",
	$220940: 'Hold your fire and wait for my command.',
	$220950: 'OPEN FIRE!',
	$220960: 'Get off the road – NOW!',
	$220970: 'OPEN FIRE!',
	$220980: 'The road’s secured from here to Omaha Beach.',
	$220990: 'Hope Able Company appreciates what we’ve done for ‘em, sir.',
	$221000: 'They will, Sergeant Carota...',
	$221010: 'They will.',
	$221020:
		'The airborne landings were scattered all across their drop-zones. Units were separated.',
	$221030:
		'It was chaos. It took some men three days to find their outfits, and some were never found.',
	$221040:
		'But even so, they took the Germans completely by surprise and secured all roads to the beaches.',
	$221050:
		'Their next objective was the crossroad town of Carentan that linked Omaha and Utah beaches...',
	$221060:
		'To prevent the Axis from driving a wedge between the allied beachheads, the town of Carentan must be captured.',
	$221070: 'We will approach from the north and move into the center of town.',
	$221080: 'The church is our first objective.',
	$221090: "Once we take the church, it'll serve as our Field HQ.",
	$221100: 'Now, we expect 6th Fallschirmjager Regiment to fanatically defend the Town Square.',
	$221110: 'When we secure the square, Carentan will be under our control.',
	$222000: 'Southern road sector captured',
