	$222220: "O'Malley's squad is pinned down!  Give 'em some covering fire!",
	$222230: 'Man that Anti-Aircraft Gun! We can use the extra FIREPOWER.',
	$222240: 'AA site neutralized! On to the next one, men!',
	$222241: "First Squad, capture that  point and let's get out of here!",
	$222250: "That's one AA down. Three more to go.",
