	$230010:
		'I’m telling ya... Yankees and Cubs, Game One, Thirty-Eight World Series. Lefty Gomez was the winning pitcher!',
	$230030: 'So, who do you think it was?',
	$230040: 'I don’t know.  Ruffing, maybe?',
	$230041: 'Hey Lewis, aren’t you a lefty too? Heh heh',
	$230050: 'I love a man with conviction.',
	$230060:
		'Well hell, I don’t know!  My kid brother would though.  He’s a damned baseball encyclopedia.',
	$230070: 'I guess being dull runs in the family!',
	$230071: "Ain't that right!",
	$230083:
		"Alright pipe down and spread out... and keep your eyes open people, we're entering enemy territory",
