	$230320: 'We can expect some pretty heavy fire coming from these locations:',
	$230321: 'Use Satchel Charges or heavy weapons to blow these buildings',
	$230330: "Let's use the buildings to cover our advance and try to flank the Germans. Understood?",
	$230340:
		'Once we have eliminated all resistance and occupied the church, we can establish a Field Barracks.',
	$230350: 'This will allow us to call in reinforcements.',
	$230360: 'Remember, keep moving and let’s take that church as fast as possible.',
