	$230560: 'First squad, in the Church!  Establish a Field Barracks.',
	$230570: 'All Clear! Cease fire!',
	$230580: 'Excellent work men.',
	$230581:
		'Elements of the 6th Fallschirmjager Regiment have set up a strongpoint here, at the center of Carentan.',
	$230582: 'Our job is to clear them out of there and capture the town hall.',
	$230583:
		'The Germans will be expecting us, so count on the main road being defended and fortified. Might be worth probing their flanks for another way in.',
	$230584:
		"We'll need reinforcements before we make our push. Our supply is pretty limited now - we can improve it by securing the strategic points around the church.",
	$230585: 'Good luck.',
	$230899: "All right. Church is over. Let's take this show to city hall.",
