	$250280: 'We have failed to relieve Dog Company',
	$250281: 'Allied field HQ is located here.',
	$250282: 'Set up a base of operations and call in reinforcements.',
	$250290: "Alright Able, word from HQ is that it's up to us to clear the road to Cherbourg.",
	$250300: 'Capture the following strategic points and defend them at all cost.',
	$250320: 'Use Engineers to expand our base and call in additional reinforcements.',
	$250321: "Without this road, the Redball Express isn't going anywhere.  Let's get to work.",
	$250325: "Okay, we gotta secure that crossroad. Let's go",
	$250326: 'We have the crossroad. Crossroad is secure.',
	$250327:
		"As of now, this road's an army road - no krauts allowed. Let's keep our road open, people.",
	$250328: "Ain't no way we're letting the krauts take our road back.",
	$250329: "We lost a sector.  Our road's not secure.  Get it back!",
	$250330: 'We need to capture those strategic points.  We need fuel and munitions.',
	$250331: 'Able Company, lead elements of the Redball Express is inbound',
	$250332:
		"The convoy will assemble here before its final leg to Cherbourg. It's our job to break any attack on those trucks. This convoy MUST get through.",
	$250333: "A lot depends on this. I know you won't let us down.",
	$250334: "You heard the Captain. The krauts won't touch the Redball Express, will they?",
	$250335: 'Here comes the convoy.',
	$250336: "Looks like they're strung out and in need of repairs.",
	$250337: 'Our route is clear.  Redball Express is moving out.',
	$250338: "We'll be ready when you are, don't you worry none.",
	$250340: 'We’ve captured the main intersection',
	$250341: 'The convoy is taking fire.',
	$250343: "Krauts are moving to hit the convoy. We gotta stop'em.",
	$250344: "C'mon people! We gotta secure our road and get that convoy through.",
	$250346: "Able Company, we're coming under fire!",
	$250347: 'Convoy requesting fire support!',
	$250350: 'Keep pushing forward!  We need to get this road secure.',
	$250353: "We've lost the lead elements of the Redball Express",
	$250360: 'Capture and hold all key sectors.',
	$250370: 'We need a Tank Depot to call in Shermans',
