		'Elements of the Panzer Lehr division are using this compound to launch attacks on the road.',
	$250411: 'The krauts are counterattacking!',
	$250412: "They're attacking the convoy!",
	$250413: 'The Krauts are hitting the Redball Express!',
	$250415: 'Panzers on the road!',
	$250420: 'Destroy their production facilities to prevent them from reinforcing.',
	$250441: 'Alright. We secured the road.',
	$250442: "Redball, you're clear to proceed.",
	$250450: 'Sir, all the men are accounted for.',
	$250470: 'Let’s find some wheels and get moving...',
	$250480: 'Sir? You OK?',
	$250490: 'Yeah. I’m fine Conti, never mind.',
	$250500: 'Let’s go.',
	$250510: 'The Red Ball Express meant ‘Priority Freight’.  Lots of it.',
	$250520: 'We must have trucked a million tons of supplies up that goddamn road.',
	$250530:
		'But Jerry wasn’t about to let his key port city go without a fight.  And fight, he did.',
	$250540: 'The 9th and 79th will be making the attack from the south, supported by the 4th cav.',
	$250550:
		'Able and Dog companies will be central to the assault, striking directly at the main docks.',
	$250560: 'This will be the most heavily defended part of the city.',
	$250570: 'We can expect some heavy resistance.',
	$251001: 'Stand by for orders.',
	$251002: 'This should be a simple operation...',
	$251003:
		'...at least one of these two roads must be secured. That means moving up and setting up defenses to cover the Red Ball Express.',
	$251004: 'The road is not secure.  HQ is pulling out.',
	$251005: "Roger that Able, see y'all in Cherbourg!",
