	$260050: 'Spread out... and keep your eyes peeled.',
	$260060: "Hey, why is it Able Company's always up front getting shot at first?",
	$260070: 'Naw Johnson, it’s not Able it just you up front getting shot at first!',
	$260080: '<laughter>',
	$260090: 'Shut up! You’re going to get us all killed.',
	$260100: 'SNIPER!!!',
	$260110: 'TAKE COVER!!',
	$260120: 'Snipers!',
	$260130: 'Squads, get your men moving and into cover!',
	$260140: 'We need support here, call in mortars.',
	$260150: 'Sniper is down.',
	$260160: 'Sniper is down.  We got the bastard.',
	$260170:
		"Cherbourg is surrounded.  They know it and we know it, but the kraut's division won’t surrender.",
	$260190:
		'The USS Texas is waiting offshore to provide fire support.  To allow it to come within range, we need to destroy the coastal gun battery located here.',
	$260200:
		'But first we need to capture this square so the Engineers can set up a forward base of operations.',
	$260201: 'Regiment wants us to secure the Town Square so we can establish our base there.',
	$260202: "Let's get it done!",
	$260203: 'Garrison one of these buildings so we can requisition some more troops.',
	$260204: 'Secure that territory to improve our supplies',
	$260210: 'Backup is here! Wooohooo!',
	$260220: 'Yeah, that’s right you Krauts, run!',
	$260230: 'Holy shit! Panzerschrecks!',
	$260240: 'Sherman’s down!',
	$260241: 'Look out! Ostwind inbound!',
	$260242: "Jerry's on the run!  Keep firing!",
	$260243: 'The Germans are retreating.',
	$260244: "Alright! They're pulling back.",
	$260250: 'The square is secure',
	$260260: 'Square secured.  The Engineers are on their way',
	$260270: 'The square is ours',
	$260280: 'The Germans are on their heels',
	$260290:
		'We’re going to need to drive hard all the way to their main garrison at the port facility and take it out',
	$260300: '*CUT*',
	$260350: 'Those are hardened bunkers!  Use satchels or demolitions to take them out!',
	$260360: 'Get some Engineers up there!',
	$260362: 'Coastal Battery breached.  Target the magazine to knock the guns out.',
	$260363: "The door's blown!  Target the magazine!",
	$260438: "Thank you ABLE, we're already on station. Your fire mission is inbound.",
	$260439:
		'Able Company to USS Texas. The coastal battery has been silenced. You may approach and fire at will!',
	$260440: 'FUCK! STOP!! SHIT!',
	$260450: 'ENOUGH! STOOOOOOOP!',
	$260451: 'TAKE COVER!',
	$260452: 'misc. soft whimperings',
	$260453: 'no, please, no more..',
	$260460: 'We’re under heavy fire here!',
	$260470: 'We’re taking heavy fire from across the canal!',
	$260490: 'Without armor, it’s murder to stay in the open.',
	$260491: 'That German officer is spotting for their artillery.',
	$260492: 'Take out that officer and we can silence their guns',
	$260493: 'Look out! Incoming!',
	$260494: "That did it. Without a spotter, their artillery shouldn't give us any more grief",
	$260495: 'Artillery spotter eliminated.  Good work Able Company.',
	$260531: 'The Germans are reinforcing their armor from the south.',
	$260532: "Until we take out their motorpool, our flank won't be secure.",
	$260533: "There's the Motorpool. Destroy it, and we can cut off their armor support",
	$260534: 'Excellent! The motorpool is destroyed.',
	$260535: "We've secured a forward Motorpool.",
	$260621: 'The pier is secure. Well done!',
	$260623: 'The north pier is destroyed. The port is crippled.',
	$260631: 'German demolition teams are placing explosive charges on the north pier',
	$260632: 'We need this port intact.',
	$260641: 'The Krauts are never going to give up unless we destroy their command structure',
	$260642: "We've got to bring the whole HQ complex down on their heads.",
	$260644: "Don't stop attacking until every every building is reduced to rubble.",
	$260650: 'This is it, they’ve got nowhere to go',
	$260660: "We’ve got 'em  between the devil and the deep blue sea.",
	$260670: 'Alright keep moving...',
	$260680: "…that's it, let's go...",
	$260690: '...that’s right Fritz, war’s over. Let’s go...',
	$260700: 'Sergeant Conti, HQ has something special for us, we’re moving out.',
	$260710: 'I’ve been told we captured over 40,000 German prisoners in Cherbourg.',
	$260720:
		'It was hard to accept that we fought so hard for this port, and all we got was a huge ruin.',
	$260730: 'The Germans had destroyed it so badly that it was months before we could use it.',
	$260740: 'Taking the city did have its perks though...',
	$260750: 'Hidden in a bunker we found secret Nazi documents...',
	$260760: 'Here are schematics of the actual V2 rocket itself.',
	$260770: 'The launch base is hidden in a valley to the south near the town of Sottevast.',
	$260780: 'It appears to be half buried in the hillside and is still under construction.',
	$260791: 'The launch platform itself is heavily defended, ruling out a direct bomber strike',
	$260792: 'Therefore this will be an airborne operation.',
	$260793:
		'After nightfall, we will land paratroopers within the perimeter walls of the base and assault the launch platform on foot.',
	$260794: 'This is a highly dangerous mission.  Godspeed.',
