	$270390: 'RUN!',
	$270400: 'the whole place is going to blow!',
	$270420: 'It was disturbing to see how far advanced the Nazi war machine had come.',
	$270430: 'Smart as our guys were, we had nothing like this...',
	$270440:
		'With Cherbourg secured Supreme Allied Command has identified our next priority: the crossroad town of Saint Lo.',
	$270450: 'Now the only place we can cross the river Vire is right here:',
	$270460: 'Unfortunately, we have very limited intelligence on this area...',
	$270461: 'Able Company will move in after dawn.',
	$270500: 'Our main target is the V2 launch platform located here.',
	$270510: 'Planting demolition charges will create a chain reaction destroying the base.',
	$270520:
		'The base is protected by Anti Aircraft guns. These limit where we can drop our paratroopers.',
	$270530: 'Take out those guns quickly to open up our dropzones.',
	$270540: "To ensure our supply lines, we'll need a secondary attack here, at the main entrance.",
	$270550: 'Understand: we will have no base of operations.',
	$270560: 'This means we need to raid enemy depots to capture heavy weapons.',
	$270570: "Let's get to it.",
	$270710: 'If we can hold the entrance, we can establish a supply line.',
	$270720:
		'The longer we keep that supply line open, the more time we give Able Company to send in reinforcements.',
	$270730: 'Now move in, and capture that strategic point.',
