	$310001: '403rd British division here.',
	$310002: '3rd Canadian division here.',
	$310003: "We don't need all that muscle.",
	$310004: 'Captain-Lieutenant! That MG has got us fixed real well!',
	$310005:
		'3rd Division this is the 403rd requesting backup; we need you to flank the building and take out the MG squad north of our current position.',
	$310006: 'Take cover to the right of that building!',
	$310007: 'Hold this position, we seem to be safe from the MG here.',
	$310008: 'Satchel that fat knacker!',
	$310009: 'Where did that Tiger pole-up from? We need to send these honkers back to Bavaria',
	$310010: "I staring that thing right down it's bloody barrel!",
	$310011: 'Christopher is down! Medic!',
	$310012: 'Darwin!!!!!!',
	$310013: 'That manky thing is going to crush us right down to our shreddies.',
	$310014: "Flippin' wonderful. Now it's going to shot us.",
	$310015: "At least here we're out of that Tiger's eye.",
	$310016:
		"Captain-Lieutenant! Let's grab that heavy weapon and give that Tiger a goffer right to the barrel.",
	$310017: 'Damn thing is heavy.',
	$310018: "Let's give ‘em some of that Carpiquet love, straight from the Candian 3rd.",
	$310019: 'This side works too, but I meant the other side.',
	$310020: '3rd Division, I told you to satchel the building, not run right into their nest.',
	$310021: 'Ping that Bazooka',
	$310022: "Jerry's got a Panzerschrek coming for us!",
	$310023: 'Looks like someone left a MP44 lying about.',
	$310024: "This church is would make a great Puzzle Palace, that's HQ to all you commonwealthers.",
	$310025: 'Captain-Lieutenant, sir!',
	$310026: 'Soldier! Where is the rest of your squad?',
	$310027: 'My orders where to hold this postion, sir.',
	$310028: "Tell your squad leader I'm going to run ashore for a bit.",
	$310029: "Here's my ride.",
	$310030: 'Yippie ki ya ay!!!!',
	$310031: 'Captain-Lieutenant, sir!',
