	$319101: 'Destroy the Tiger',
	$319102:
		'XXXX Regiment is holding back our armour until we neutralize those artillery emplacements.',
	$319103: 'XXXX Once the guns are destroyed we can continue the attack.',
	$319104: 'XXXX Good job! One of the Nebelwerfer locations has been cleared.',
	$319105: 'XXXX Well done! The guns have been destroyed.',
	$319106: 'XXXX Regiment has sent us some reinforcements.',
	$319107: 'XXXX Time to advance. Proceed with caution.',
	$319108: 'Nebelwerfer Battery',
	$319109: 'Destroyed Nebelwerfer Battery',
	$319200: 'Rescue the Wounded',
	$319201:
		'Build AID STATION. Then get a COMMANDER to lead the pinned squads back to the AID STATION.',
	$319202: 'XXXX Elements of the 1st and 2nd rifle squads have been pinned down by the artillery.',
	$319203: "XXXX They've taken a pounding and are pretty shaken up.",
	$319204: 'XXXX Get a COMMANDER out there, get them on their feet and get their heads straight.',
	$319205: "XXXX Our boys are pinned. They're taking a beating!",
	$319206: "XXXX We gotta get them outa there before they're all lost!",
	$319207: "XXXX We have to save our wounded! They're almost gone.",
	$319208: 'XXXX Forget it COMMANDER, we lost them.',
	$319209: 'XXXX Good work! We saved all of the pinned squads.',
	$319210: 'XXXX We saved most of our pinned boys.',
	$319211: 'XXXX Well at least we saved some of them.',
	$319212: 'Wounded Soldiers',
	$319301:
		'Victory is ours //Eliminate the defending Nazis or force them into retreat and claim the town square.',
	$319302:
		"XXXX Command wants us to take the town of St. Lo but the Nazis are pretty well dug in. It's gonna be a helluva fight!",
	$319303:
		"XXXX Only after we kick the krauts out and claim the town square can we call this city 'cleared'.",
	$319304: "XXXX Holy Hell! They've got themselves walled in with some heavy fire power.",
	$319305: 'XXXX A frontal assault would be suicide.',
	$319306: 'XXXX We must probe the line and look for a weakness.',
	$319307: "XXXX We have the perimeter well secured. Now it's time to take the town square.",
	$319308:
		"XXXX It's awfully quiet in there. Advance to the town square, but proceed with caution.",
	$319309: 'XXXX The town of St. Lo is liberated!',
	$319310: 'XXXX Mission Complete // Destroy Axis HQ (Mission Complete)',
	$319400: 'Surround the Axis HQ',
	$319401:
		'The remaining Axis defenders have fortified St. Lo and will only surrender when all the Strategic Points surrounding the Town Center have been captured.',
	$319402: 'XXXX The Nazis have heavily fortified the main road but left their flanks exposed.',
	$319403:
		'XXXX If we claim all the TERRITORIES surrounding the town square we can pour on the pain from every direction.',
	$319404: 'XXXX Outstanding! The town square has been completely cut off.',
	$319500: 'Join Forces',
	$319501:
		'XXXX Regiment has informed us that elements of COMPANY A and B have moved in from the North and South of St. Lo.',
	$319502: 'XXXX We have allied forces approaching our position from the North and the South.',
	$319503:
		"XXXX If we can capture the TERRITORIES preventing their advance, we're sure to get some help taking this town!",
	$319504: "XXXX Good work! There's A COMPANY. Let's give'em a hand with their gear.",
	$319505: "XXXX Excellent! There's B COMPANY. Looks like they have ammo to spare!",
	$319506: "XXXX Looks like we're all here. Let's go get those bastards.",
	$319507: 'North Road Territory',
	$319508: 'South Road Territory',
	$319600: 'Promote Rangers',
	$319601: 'Ensure at least on Ranger Squad is promoted to Rank Three Veterans.',
	$319602:
		'XXXX The Nazis are using the main roads heading east to keep the town supplied with men and armour.',
	$319603:
		'XXXX If we take the supply roads we can starve the Nazis of their precious reinforcements.',
	$319604: "XXXX Oooh Rah! We've taken one of the roads.",
	$319605: 'XXXX Bang-on! All the Nazi supply lines have been cut.',
	$319606: 'XXXX Northeast Supply Road',
	$319607: 'XXXX Southeast Supply Road',
	$319608: 'XXXX That was too easy. Be prepared for a counter attack.',
	$319609: "XXXX This position is too important to loose. Dig in. They'll be back.",
	$319700: "XXXX All right, let's move out!",
	$319701: "XXXX Don't stand there in the open, find some cover!",
	$319702: 'XXXX Press the attack! Move it, move it, move it!',
	$319703: "XXXX The Nazi bastards are retreating! They're retreating!",
	$319704: 'XXXX Another TERRITORY is ours! Keep it up!',
	$319705: 'XXXX Look at them run. Filthy cowards!',
	$319706: "XXXX We gott'em on the run boys! Pour it on!",
	$319707: "XXXX They're pulling back. Quickly, advance!",
	$319708: "XXXX Hit'em with everything you got!",
