	$320466: 'Kill confirmed, Panther Target.',
	$320467: 'Kill confirmed, Panther Target.',
	$320470: 'Panther is reloading, move! move! move!',
	$320475: 'Panther is attacking us, disperse!',
	$320480: "Enemy Panther... he's got us square in his sights",
	$320485: 'Kraut armor inbound...',
	$320490: 'Gunner Target that Panther...',
	$320520: 'Listen up, we NEED those M10s to the front... NOW',
	$320530: 'Call up the M10s...',
	$320540: 'You heard the Captain, get more M10s into the fight!',
	$320550: "Use those smoke canisters Those Panther's can't hit what he can't see.",
	$320560: 'Nothing is getting through their FRONT armor, we have to FLANK those Panthers.',
	$320570: 'If we can sneak around behind him, we can hit him from the rear.',
	$320580: 'We need those M10 tank destroyers to take out the PANTHERS',
	$320600: 'AMBUSH... Panther closing in!',
	$320610: "Look out! They're using Goliaths!",
	$320620: 'Smokescreen! Prepare for contact!',
	$320630: "Support! We're under attack by multiple Panthers!",
	$320650: "We've lost sight of the panther!",
	$320660: 'Scout the area before the Panther flanks us.',
	$320700: 'Panther is down!',
	$320710: 'Hella ya, way to go Able company!',
	$320720: "Yessir, that's from Uncle Sam with love!",
	$320730: 'Woo Hoo! Look at him burn! Take that you Kraut',
	$320740: 'Nothing but a smoking wreck!',
	$320750: "That's one less Panther to worry about",
	$321060:
		"Our M10s are fast and pack a punch, but they can't go toe-to-toe with a Panther.  Go for the side or rear armor.",
	$321070:
		"Air recon shows the Panthers were last spotted in this area and we can presume they're waiting for us.",
	$321080:
		"We're outgunned here and those Panthers have the element of surprise. So proceed with caution.",
	$321081:
		"Once we've located the Panthers, use Shermans and infantry to draw them out and then deploy M10 Tank Destroyers to flank them.",
	$323001:
		'Alright, the Panzer Lehr took a beating this morning, but its Panther tanks are still operational and a threat to us.',
	$325100: 'Gunner, stand by.',
	$325101: 'Range: eight hundred and fifty meters.',
	$325102: 'Target: American officers... six, two, three degrees',
	$325103: 'Fire when ready...',
	$325104: 'MEDIC! MEDIC!! We need a fucking medic!!',
	$325105: 'The area is NOT secured. Set up a defensive perimeter now.',
	$325106: 'Spencer…',
	$325109: 'Conti! Just the man I need to talk to.  Alright..',
	$325200: 'Some officers never earn your respect.',
	$325201: 'Captain MacKay had mine from day one.  Boot camp, Fort Reilly, Kansas.',
	$325202: "I knew he'd keep us alive.",
	$325203: "We're being redeployed off the front lines to the town of Mortain.",
	$325204: 'We will relieve Dog Company who are holding Hill three-seventeen.',
	$325205: 'Lieutenant Conti is now in command.',
	$329022: 'Destroy all Panther Tanks',
	$329030: 'Panther',
	$329031:
		"The surviving Panthers of Panzer Lehr division have withdrawn to this area. Able Company's orders are to hunt down and destroy the remaining Panther Tanks.",
	$329040: 'Able Company',
	$329041: 'Panzer Lehr Division',
	$329100: 'Goliath Attacking!',
	$329101: 'Goliath',
	$329102: 'Base Under Attack!',
	$329103: 'Flanked From Behind!',
	$329104: 'Panzer Flanking!',
	$329110: 'Lost Sight of Panther',
	$329111: 'Panther Destroyed!',
	$329112: 'Panther Attacking!',
	$329200: 'Minimize Tank Casualties',
	$329201: "HQ's orders are to limit tank losses for this operation.",
	$329205: 'Allied Tank Lost!',
	$329300: 'M10 Tank Destroyer',
	$329301: 'New M10 Tank Destroyer Available',
	$329350: 'Start',
	$329351: 'One Panther Defeated',
	$329352: 'Two Panthers Defeated',
	$329353: 'Three Panthers Defeated',
	$329354: 'Four Panthers Defeated',
	$329355: 'Five Panthers Defeated',
	$329356: 'Six Panthers Defeated',
	$330001: 'Hi Taggart',
	$330002: 'Hey listen, Conti, sorry about MacKay.',
	$330003: 'Try and get some R&R on this hill, should be a piece of cake.',
	$330004: "Taggart, Let's go.",
	$330005: 'Franks! This hole ain’t gonna dig itself!',
	$330006: 'Get your ass over here!',
	$330007: 'I heard you guys served together since boot camp back in Kansas...',
	$330010: 'Hey, can you see something out there?',
	$330011: 'I thought I saw something...',
	$330012: 'CONTACT!!!',
	$338100: 'Hold the line! We got krauts on our hill!',
	$338101: 'Fritz is on our hill! Hold them back!',
	$338110: 'Incoming! To the trenches! We gotta hold this hill!',
	$338120: 'We got incoming! Hold the line!',
	$338130: 'When the shelling stops, prepare for a counterattack.',
	$338140: "They're coming! Another wave! Ready defense!",
	$338941:
		'Well, so much for the cake-walk. We have elements of the 2nd Panzer division moving in.',
	$338942: 'Our secondary objective is to hold the town of Mortain.',
	$338943: "If we lose Mortain, we'll be completely surrounded.",
	$338944: 'Goddammit, just  hold out til dawn.',
	$338945:
		"Okay, we can not lose this hill. It just can't happen. We gotta hold the line or all hell's gonna break loose.",
	$338950: "We've lost the hill!  We gotta get it back!",
	$338960: "Okay, it's pretty simple. We gotta hold hill 317 'til oh six thirty",
	$338961:
		"And that's all. Dog Company will be here with armor and, hopefully, coffee at oh-six-thirty.",
	$338962: 'We need to set up a defensive perimeter.',
	$338963:
		"Dog company put some emplacements in, but nobody's manning those positions now. Let's get some squads out there.",
	$338964: 'Once our perimeter is established, we need to fortify the town of Mortain.',
	$338970: "Stand to!  Stand to!  The hill's under attack!",
	$338971: 'Our whole damn perimeter is vulnerable.',
	$338972:
		"We've gotta reinforce the line now. Get some MG nests and barbed wire on those approaches.",
	$338980: "They're at Mortain! Krauts are attacking the town!",
	$338981: 'Krauts are trying to take Mortain. We gotta push them back.',
	$338990: "Krauts are in the wire! They're hitting our HQ!",
	$338991: "They've taken out our headquarters! We are losing!",
