		'A squad of Rangers is pinned down in the Abbey Blanche, rescue them before they are killed!',
	$339933: 'Mission Failed: Hill 317 is Lost',
	$339934: 'Failed to hold Strategic Point on Hill 317',
	$339940: 'NIS13_01 "Able relieves Dog"',
	$339941: 'NIS13_02 "Flares"',
	$339943: "Don't let the Axis capture the central point in Mortain.",
	$339982: 'Recapture Mortain!',
	$340001: 'This is Echo-Bravo five-six-five.',
	$340002: 'Target acquired, I’m starting my run, over.',
	$340100: "Okay, now we got reinforcements, we're gonna push those krauts off our damn hill.",
	$340110:
		"If we can capture and hold these strategic points, those panzers won't have no choice but to retreat.",
	$340121: "Okay, 'nough talking. Let's get to work.",
	$340200:
		"Those 88's are pounding us into hamburger. Knocking 'em out would make this day go a hell of a lot smoother.",
	$340211: "OK,listen up: a carton o' smokes for whoever puts the kebosh to those damn 88s",
	$340400: 'Gotta minefield here!  Get a Sherman crab to clear this up.',
	$340410: "We stumbled on a minefield. Where's our Sherman crab?",
	$340420: 'Enemy minefield. Can we get this cleared?',
	$340600: 'Able, this is Dog Company.  How was that R&R?  You guys all rested up?',
	$340601: "I'll bet you loved it up on that hill huh?",
	$340602: 'I hope you kept our hill in good shape',
	$340603: 'I hope you took care of our hill.',
	$340604:
		"Dog, just get that fucking armor into position.  Those krauts aren't gonna wait for you.",
	$340700: "Krauts are probing 'round the Abbey. Let's lock it down.",
	$340710: "We're taking fire at the fields to the northeast. We gotta rally some defense.",
	$340720: "Fritz is trying to take our hill. Let's push them back.",
	$340730: 'Krauts are hitting Mortain. We gotta hold that town.',
	$340740: 'Enemy action at the farmhouse. Farmhouse is under attack.',
	$340751: 'Captain Shultz survived the destruction of the Panzer Lehr division.',
	$340753:
		'Battle reports show his Tigergroupen has knocked out 17 allied tanks and destroyed Baker Company.',
	$340754: 'With those Tigers in position, we can’t cut off the German retreat.',
	$340755: 'He must be removed.',
	$349040: 'Able Company',
	$349041: '7th Army Regiment',
	$349042: 'Dog Company',
	$349420: 'Capture and hold 3 Victory Points',
	$349425: 'Destroy Flak 88 Batteries',
	$349428: 'Win with more than 250 Points',
	$349430:
		"Able's orders are to push the Panzer formations out of Mortain. Capture and hold the indicated Victory Points surrounding Hill 317 to secure Mortain.",
	$349440: 'The Axis have set up a number of 88 batteries. Destroy them all.',
	$349441: 'The Allies Victory Points cannot fall below 250 to win a decisive victory.',
	$349460: 'Able Company',
