	$359934: 'Allied Base Destroyed',
	$360001: "This is Echo-Bravo five-six-five. I see'em.  They're like sittin' ducks, all lined up.",
	$360002: 'Whoo-hoo!',
	$360003: 'Alright we’re going to make a second pass... stand by...',
	$360005: 'Attention Able Company, convoy destroyed',
	$360006: 'We’ll be on station, call us anytime!',
	$360020: 'Troop convoys from the German 7th Army are retreating along these roads.',
	$360021: "This is their last escape route. It's out job to close it.",
	$360030:
		'To cut them off, we gotta link our territory with the Canadians and Polish to our north.',
	$360031:
		'As we advance, secure these bridges. This will bottleneck the Germans and slow down their retreat.',
	$360032: 'Alright Able Company, this is it.',
	$360070: 'Ok, territory is secured.',
	$360071: 'Territories linked.',
	$360108: "Look at 'em run!",
	$360109: 'Yah lousy huns! Come back and fight!',
	$360110:
		"Recon tells us we have incoming Panzers.  They're going to try to break through our lines.",
	$360112:
		"We've closed the Falaise pocket.  Before we break out the cigars, we got some more work to do.",
	$360113:
		"Those Panzers are the last of the German resistance.  If we can knock 'em out, the German 7th Army's as good as dead.",
	$360130: 'Too many German convoys are escaping, we need to link up with our allies NOW!',
	$360140: 'We gotta close the gap NOW - too many krauts are slipping through.',
	$360180: "We've secured all the bridges. The krauts are cut off.",
	$360181: "Now let's focus on linking up our sectors with our allies.",
	$360189: "Alright Jerry let's MOVE IT!",
	$360190: "Secure and hold those bridges.  That'll slow down the Axis retreat.",
	$360192: "Let's go...",
	$360195: 'Hey, how come they get to celebrate and we get stuck with this bum job?',
	$360196: 'Relax Taggart, let ‘em have their fun. They earned it...',
	$360197: '...and besides, look at all these new friends you have!',
	$360198: 'You just have to get to know them better, that’s all...',
	$360199: 'Sir! What you doin’ over there?',
	$360200: "They've taken a bridge!",
	$360201: "They're attacking the bridges!",
	$360202: 'Air Strike!  Take Cover!',
	$360203: 'Air Strike!  Where is the Luftwaffe?!',
	$360204: 'Convoy under attack!',
	$360205: 'Convoy under fire!',
	$360206: 'We must keep the roads open!',
	$360207: "We're losing!",
	$360208: "We'll never get out of here alive!",
	$360209: "This isn't fair!",
	$360210: 'How can there be so many of them!?',
	$360211: "There's no where to go!",
	$360212: 'We should surrender!',
