	$369024: "You've won the battle of Chambois and closed the Falaise pocket",
	$369025: 'Axis Convoy Sighted!',
	$369030:
		'Link the southern territory sectors with the Canadian frontlines to the north. Capture the indicated Points to close the Falaise Pocket in time!',
	$369031: 'Destroy Axis Convoys',
	$369032:
		'Maintain the territory connection and stop the Germans from punching a hole through the territory line; make sure to destroy all enemy armor.',
	$369033:
		"Destroy all retreating Axis Convoys before they escape through Chambois. Controlling the bridges will limit the Convoy's escape routes.",
	$369034: 'Capture this Bridge',
	$369035: 'Connect Territory Allied Forces.',
