	$407550: 'Welcome to training, Kampfgruppe Lehr is standing by.',
	$407551:
		'During this exercise, you will learn about the unique aspects of the Panzer Elite and their arsenal of vehicles.',
	$407552:
		"You'll learn how to attack from halftracks, to capture and secure territory with vehicles, to resupply with the Munitions Halftrack, and to lock-down vehicles.",
	$407553: "Let's start by upgrading a squad of Panzer Grenadiers with Panzerschrecks.",
	$407554:
		'Kampfgruppe Lehr has heard reports of enemy infantry in the area.  We need to scout their position.',
	$407556:
		'LEFT-CLICK on the flashing button on the Command Panel to upgrade the squad with a Panzerschreck.',
	$407557:
		'Panzer Grenadiers are the backbone of any Panzer Elite army, they are versatile and able to respond to any enemy threats.',
	$407558: 'Good job, you successfully upgraded your Panzer Grenadier squad.',
	$407559: 'Garrison that Halftrack, we need to move out.',
	$407560: 'RIGHT-CLICK the Halftrack to order your Panzer Grenadiers to get inside.',
	$407561:
		'Panzer Elite infantry garrisoned in open-topped vehicles can shoot out the back with any equipped weapons.',
	$407562: 'Halftrack and Panzer Grenadiers are ready for action.',
	$407563: 'Your Panzer Grenadiers have vacated the halftrack. Order them back into the halftrack.',
	$407564:
		"The Panzer Grenadiers are not only transported with the vehicle, but they add additional firepower to the halftrack's own machine gun.",
	$407565: 'Notice that one of the squad members is carrying a Panzerschreck.',
	$407566: 'Enemy infantry spotted. Move out and attack them.',
	$407567: 'Order your halftrack to attack the indicated squad by RIGHT-CLICKING on it.',
	$407568: 'Panzerschreck opening fire!',
	$407569: 'Enemy infantry defeated!',
	$407570: 'Look out! Counter-attack!',
	$407571: "We're taking too much damage, we need more firepower! Get a grenade on that infantry.",
	$407572: 'Additional reinforcements available. Select the new Panzer Grenadier squad.',
	$407573: 'LEFT-CLICK the flashing button to UNLOAD your squad from the Halftrack.',
	$407574: 'LEFT-CLICK on the the flashing GRENADE ICON in the Command Panel.',
	$407575: 'Target the infantry, and LEFT-CLICK on them to throw the grenade.',
	$407576: 'Excellent!',
	$407577:
		"Panzer Grenadiers use INCENDIARY GRENADES. These grenades don't do much initial damage, but entrenched squads will burn if they stay put.",
	$407579: 'You missed! Try again!',
	$407580: 'Enemy infantry neutralized!',
	$407581: 'First, LEFT-CLICK on the Panzer Grenadier squad to select them.',
