	$1322010: 'Use the walking barrage to support infantry on their way up.',
	$1322020: "Keep a look out for enemy emplacements Jerry knows we're coming.",
	$1322030: 'Jerry Contact, flank that emplacement and take it out lads!',
	$1322040: 'A-V-R-E support required, I say again A-V-R-E support required.',
	$1322041: "We've got heavy concrete bunkers!",
	$1322050: "You've got the location now get to it!",
	$1322060: "I'll be fucked mate if I make half way up this forsaken hill!",
	$1322070: "Cover me Nathan, I'm going in!",
	$1322080: 'Mark my words! This hill will be in Allied hands by nightfall!',
	$1322090: 'Sweet Mary mother of Christ!',
	$1322100: 'They killed fucking Darwin, those bastards!',
	$1322110: 'Poor guy just wanted to show the world a bit of good.',
