	$1322170: 'Find cover!  Incoming!',
	$1322180: "Jerry's got arty on the hill!",
	$1322190: 'Gun Line!  Fire mission!  Walking barrage!  H-E quick, stand by!',
	$1322200: 'Extend line gents!  Arty inbound!  Move, move!',
	$1322210: 'Be ready to go once the rounds start to splash down!',
	$1322220: "Walking barrage boys, artillery's gonna lead up  the hill!",
	$1322230: 'Form up on the assault line!',
	$1322240: 'Move, Move!',
	$1322250: 'Shite, shut your mouth and move!',
	$1322260: 'Arty Barrage is standing by, Major.',
	$1322270: 'Lt Bailey you are clear to commence the Walking Barrage from Tourmauville or Baron',
	$1322280: 'The Walking Barrage will cover our advance as 3rd Battalion moves up the hill.',
	$1322290: 'Form your units up in the designated area outside Tourmauville.',
	$1322300: 'Form your units up on the grid location outside Baron.',
	$1322310: 'Okay, get ready. The barrage should begin any minute now.',
	$1322320: 'Wait for the signal.',
	$1322330: 'Move! Move! Move!',
	$1322340: 'Go! Go! Go!',
	$1322350: 'Move up that line!',
	$1322360: 'Get up that hill!',
	$1322370: 'Signal spotted.',
	$1322380: 'We have a go.',
	$1322390: 'Heads down, next barrage imminent!',
	$1322400: 'Hold onto your knickers, lads!',
	$1322410: 'Incoming barrage.',
	$1322420: 'Walking Barrage available.',
	$1322430: 'Artillery bunker spotted, eliminate the threat.',
	$1322440: "We'll do no good with that Turret on us, take it out!",
	$1322450: "And take out those sodding pillboxes while you're at it!",
	$1322460: "We're getting close, button it up and take that hill!",
	$1322470: 'Look what we dug up on the rabbit run!',
	$1322480: 'Made a block of Swiss cheese out this hill they did!',
	$1322490: "I thought she was a hill but this girl's a flibbin fortress!",
	$1322500: 'There must be entrances all over this hill!',
	$1322510: "It's like a rabbit warren!",
	$1322520: 'Just wait till Major Blackmore gets a load of this.',
	$1322530: 'Shite! That had to hurt.',
	$1322540: "No more Jerry in them sorry holes that's for sure.",
	$1322550: 'Jerry is a bit like a tricky rabbit. Fucking tarts.',
	$1322560: 'Jerry Artillery emplacement sighted.',
	$1322570: 'Take Cover...',
	$1322580: 'We need HE to crack that bunker.',
	$1322590: 'Contact! Static AT emplacement.',
	$1322600: "Keep those bleedin' Cromwell's out of its arcs!",
	$1322610: 'Degnan I want that turret in ruins... now!',
	$1322620: "What the hell is that fuckin' behemoth.",
	$1322630: 'Looks like a tank turret.',
	$1322640: "Fuckin' poor bastards didn't know what hit 'em.",
	$1322650: 'Is that a foot?',
	$1322651: 'Oh shite, smells like a cook out.',
	$1322660: "Panthers! They've got Panthers incoming.",
	$1322670: 'Armor support needed on the hill, Panthers spotted.',
	$1322680: 'I say again, Panthers on the Hill!',
	$1322690: "Look at 'em run!",
	$1322700: 'Jerry fell down an broke his crown, and we came tumbling after!',
	$1322710: "Looks like Jerry's got no balls at all!",
	$1322720: 'Hill 112 is finally ours, gentlemen, Bravo.',
	$1322730: 'Too much Allied blood has been shed for this hill.',
	$1322740: 'I get a message up the chain to the Major...',
	$1322750: 'Listen up men, secure the village sector in readiness for the HQ!',
	$1322760: "The destination won't have supply lines.",
	$1322770: 'Capture all the sectors at the specified grid locations.',
	$1322780: 'That bridge will need to be repaired as well.',
	$1328000: 'In the S2\'s own words, "...the hill should be clear and void of any enemy defenses."',
	$1328005:
		"Not surprisingly, the General's Intel Staff have their heads completely up their arses.",
	$1328010:
		'To reach Hill 112 we have to cross the bridges over the River Odon near the villages of Baron, and Tourmauville.',
	$1328030: 'Recce has identified elements of the 1st and 10th SS Panzer Divisions in the area.',
	$1328040: 'Churchill heavy tanks from the Royal Scots are moving up as we speak.',
	$1328050: 'Have our light Armor recce the bridges before committing the heavy tanks.',
	$1328060: '3rd Battalion must clear the villages and secure a bridgehead across the Odon.',
	$1328070: "Move quickly, I don't want to bottleneck the main advance.",
	$1328100: 'With the bridgehead established, we can advance onto Hill 112.',
	$1328110:
		'The 10th SS have firmly dug in. Division has made artillery support available to 3rd Battalion.',
	$1328120: "The divisons' Howitzers are in range and ready to provide fire support.",
	$1328130:
		'Instruct them to provide a Walking Barrage to support our advances on the Hill at these locations.',
	$1328140: "Let's soften up Jerry for the boys.",
	$1328150: 'Have the Royal Scots form up on the assault line before the attack.',
	$1328160: '3rd Battalion orders are to take the Hill.',
	$1328200: 'Initial reports indicate the Huns have defensive positions along the River Odon.',
	$1328210: 'Resistance should be limited to MG Teams, snipers and scattered AT Guns.',
	$1328220: 'Secure a base of operations, here.',
	$1328230:
		"When the perimeter has been established, deploy 3rd Battalion's Mobile HQ to the area.",
	$1328240:
		'Once on the ground, we will have additional Infantry and Light Armored support available.',
