	$1369211: 'Sector Secured',
	$1370500: "Major, Caen is in 3rd Battalion's hands.",
	$1370501: 'Charlie and Baker company are organizing defenses along our flanks.',
	$1370502: 'No major contacts have been reported south of Caen, either.',
	$1370503: 'Have the commanders establish a defensive front and await further orders.',
	$1370504: 'Division reports we can expect the weather to worsen before morning.',
	$1370510:
		'Deploy the HQ and Command Posts near the Cathedral and fortify all the major roads leading into Caen.',
	$1370520: "With this rain, we'll be hard pressed to spot a counterattack before it's too late.",
	$1370530:
		'Right. The Major wants the Battalion to shake out and reorg before pulling out in the morning.',
	$1370540:
		'Get the Command Posts into position and establish a defensive perimeter around the Cathedral.',
	$1370550: "Rain or shine, we've got a job to do.",
	$1370560: 'Leave it to the officers to have us waiting around in the fucking rain.',
	$1370570: 'Shut your gob.',
	$1370580: "Blackmore's never done anything to cock us over.",
	$1370590: "He's got a plan.",
	$1370600: "We just have to hold tight, that's all.",
	$1370610: 'Tell that to Degnan as his grave fills with water.',
	$1370620: "All my fuckin' kit's wet. You got an extra pair of socks, mate?",
	$1370630: "Fuckin' me. This cold's getting' right to the bone.",
	$1370640: "Some fuckin' wanker stole my umbrella.",
	$1370650: "Oy, I think them Canadian's have rain gear. They're never complaining' about shite.",
	$1370660: "Steady up, lads. It's just a bit of rain.",
	$1370670: "Mother nature's taken a piss of us lads. Literally.",
	$1370680: "I betcha Gladstone's kilt is soak right through to his arse!",
	$1370690: 'Reminds me of my walk-about back in the highlands.',
	$1370700: "This rain cut's right to the bone, eh' Keegan?",
	$1370710: "Soldier on, you fuckin' wanker. It's only a wee Scottish mist.",
	$1370720:
		"This ain't rain! Rain cuts through your skin and peels the meat off your bones. Now that's real rain, you puffer.",
	$1370730:
		"Quit being such a wee little school girl.  Look at them Canadians... not a fuckin' word about the rain.",
	$1370740: "Just like fuckin' rainy Vancouver, eh' troops?",
	$1370750: "At least Smithy won't fuckin' smell so bad!",
	$1370760: "Look at what I stole from one of the Brits! A fuckin' umbrella!",
	$1370770: "No wonder you're wet. Use your shelter half as a cover, you dumb fuck.",
	$1370780:
		"I betcha Jerry's sitting' cozy in some dry fuckin' bunker eating wieners and sauerkraut!",
	$1370790: 'Use your ground sheet to keep your kit dry, boys.',
	$1370800: 'Stand To! Germans on the line!',
	$1370810: "Cover off on your posts! Jerry's tryin' to push in!",
	$1370820: "Man your posts! They've mustered a counterattack!",
	$1370830: 'Major, we have a sizeable counterattack on our hands.',
	$1370840: 'SS Panzers supported by infantry should be expected from these directions.',
	$1370850:
		'The main body will most likely approach from here, however we can expect flanking attacks from all these directions.',
	$1370860: 'We need to hold onto Caen at all costs.',
	$1370870: 'Order 3rd Battalion to hold these points, no matter what.',
	$1370880:
		'Have platoon level commanders establish defensive lines around the ground they control.',
	$1370890: 'Make sure they have quick reaction forces ready to respond to areas needing support.',
	$1370900: 'We need only hold out until morning. Godspeed.',
	$1370910: "Get this out at section level. Make sure they know it's coming directly from me.",
	$1370920: 'Defend Caen... At all costs.',
	$1370930: "Show the Huns what you're made of.",
	$1370940: 'Our motto is "Doubt not" for good reason.',
	$1370950: "Let's hand Jerry his ass.",
	$1370960: "We've got movement. Steady up, lads.",
	$1370970: "Stand to. We've got Jerry on the move.",
	$1370980: 'Contact! Enemy Infantry! Platoon level assault!',
	$1370990: 'Get me some MG emplacements!',
	$1371000: "Pour it on, gents! Let 'em have it!",
	$1371010: "Soft skinned vehicles! Tear 'em up, gents!",
	$1371020: "Break out the AT and rip 'em open!",
	$1371030: "Recce vehicles! Let 'em have it, gents!",
	$1371040: 'Panzers!',
	$1371050: 'German Armor!',
	$1371060: 'Contact! Panzers!',
	$1371070: "We've got a Tiger tank over here!",
	$1371080: "Streuth! They've got Tigers!",
	$1371090: "Tigers! Jerry's got a troop of Tiger tanks!",
	$1371100: 'Incoming!',
	$1371110: 'Find some cover, gents!',
	$1371120: "That's German artillery! Find cover!",
	$1371130: "Fuckin' hell! There's too many of 'em!",
	$1371140: 'Mother loving bastards, they killed poor Darwin!',
	$1371150: "Where the fuck are all these Jerry's coming' from!?",
	$1371160: "We've got to pull back!",
	$1371170: 'Steady, mate! Just keep bloody firing!',
	$1371180: 'Covering fire! I need covering fire over here!',
	$1371190: 'Someone go for help!',
	$1371200: 'Hold your ground! Do not fall back!',
	$1371210: "Stand fast, men! Don't let them through!",
	$1371220: "Get fire on those assholes! Come on! Let 'em have it!",
	$1371230: "There's too many of 'em!",
	$1371240: "We're gonna get over run!",
	$1371250: 'Where the fuck is our support!?',
	$1371260: 'Enemy movement near the Crossroads, defend it!',
	$1371270: 'The Jerries are attacking the Crossroads.',
	$1371280: 'Crossroads under attack!',
	$1371290: 'Enemy contact near the courtyard, defend it.',
	$1371300: "3rd Battalion, we're losing contact with the Courtyard.",
	$1371310: 'Move in and repel the counterattack at the Courtyard.',
	$1371320: 'The Cathedral is under attack, request support.',
	$1371330: 'Contacts sighted near the Cathedral!',
	$1371340: "We're losing the Cathedral.",
	$1371350: "3rd Battalion's losing an objective, hold the line!",
	$1371360: "Enemy attack, we're losing ground 3rd Battalion!",
	$1371370: 'Hold the line, 3rd Battalion, recapture that point.',
	$1371380: "Tiger tank! No fuck! It's a King Tiger! Get fire on 'em!",
	$1371390: "Holy shit! We've got a King Tiger over here!",
	$1371400: "King Tiger! Hit 'em with everything you got, troops!",
	$1371410:
		'The balance of the Panzer division is on its way. Cover off on their axis of approach and cut them down, lads!',
	$1371420: "Here comes the main assault! Wait until they're in your kill-zones!",
	$1371430: "They're headed toward our HQ!",
	$1371440: "Get a QRF back on the HQ! They're going for Blackmore!",
	$1371450: "Sigs, message for Battalion. Situation resolved. The city is fuckin' ours!",
	$1371460: "That's how ya fuckin' do it troops! Caen is ours, boys!",
	$1371470:
		'Pass the word. All clear. Get Ammo-Cas reports up the chain, have NCOs set up pickets and forced rest for their troops. Move.',
	$1379100: 'Locate Enemy Forces',
	$1379101: 'Defend Caen',
	$1379102: 'Destroy the Tiger',
	$1379103: 'Eliminate the King Tiger',
	$1379110: 'Search the area to determine the strength of the Axis forces.',
	$1379111:
		'Maintain control of at least one of the key Strategic Points in the Cathedral, Crossroads or Courtyard.',
	$1379112: 'Destroy the incoming Tiger. Prevent it from attacking the HQ Command Truck.',
	$1379113: 'Encircle the King Tiger then concentrate Anti Tank fire on flanks and rear.',
