	$1418410: 'Bergetiger is in support.',
	$1418420: 'She is fitted with a winch capable of lifiting damaged tanks for repairs.',
	$1418430: 'Used wisely, the Bergetiger can recover destroyed tanks by salvaging the wreck!',
