	$6011260: 'Ready! Starting engine!',
	$6011270: 'Come on, mein Fräulein. Give Papa some love.',
	$6011280: 'Yes! You big bastard!',
	$6011290: 'Congratulations, Oberschütze Schroif. You can drive the tank for another day.',
	$6011300: 'Action stations! Prepare for contact.',
	$6011301: 'Convoy halted!',
	$6011302: 'The convoy appears to have halted.  Ready yourselves and assault the town! Schnell!',
	$6011303: 'Schroif! get this tank back to the road! We must stop the convoy.',
	$6011304: "Stop cruising about the country-side, we'll miss the convoy!",
	$6011305:
		"What are you doing Schroif?  If you don't turn this tank around this minute I'll court martial you!",
	$6011306:
		"Dumpfbacke! Hinterwäldler! Get back to the road or I'll turn your nuts into war trophies!",
	$6011307: 'Eliminate every vehicle in the convoy! Schnell!',
	$6011308:
		'Shultz! If you let another convoy vehicle pass, we might as well roll out the red carpet for the British!',
	$6011310: 'It was a red dawn the morning our Tiger Tank first arrived on the front lines.',
	$6011311: 'Convoy destroyed!',
	$6011320: '1st schwere-Panzer-Abteilung 503 reports T-34s entering our sector.',
	$6011330: 'Confirmed. Load APC rounds, halt motor.',
	$6011340: 'Hydraulic takeoff 600 P-S to turret.',
