		'That was the last time I saw the interior of a Tiger Tank, the last time I saw Shultz.',
	$6030510:
		'He went on to command the 502 Tigergruppe. On August 9th, 1944, he held the advancing Americans at Autry long enough to allow our division to escape Normandy. He died in his Tiger.',
	$6030520:
		'By September what was left of our division redeployed to Holland. I assumed command of the Panzer Lehr Division as Majorgeneral.',
	$6030521:
		'It had seemed so clear, so necessary. But in the end, Senior Command had lost its way, and unfortunately the fatherland followed.',
	$6030590: 'This is Panzergruppe Lehr, taking your lead.',
