	$9394664: '+ %1Amount% Fuel',
	$9394665: '+ %1Amount% Munition',
	$9395060: 'Hauptmann Funke has delegated responsibility to me. So listen up.',
	$9395061: 'The Americans could be here at any moment.',
	$9395062: 'They will not underestimate us again, so expect a much larger force.',
	$9395063: 'Our garrisons must be defended.',
	$9395064: 'If the battle looks grim, focus all defences around the river crossings.',
	$9395065: 'And no matter what, defend the church.',
	$9395066: 'If we lose that, all hope is lost.',
	$9395070: 'What is this? American troops!',
	$9395080: 'Without any warning?',
	$9395090: 'Leutnant Hess! Orders!',
	$9395160: 'Sir! The Americans are pressing to the east!',
	$9395170: 'Hauptmann Funke! This is not just an advance force! This is a full-out invasion!',
	$9395180: 'Hauptmann! The Americans are gaining ground! We need orders!',
	$9395190: 'Sir! We need orders! What do we do?',
	$9395200: 'The situation is dire Hauptmann, if we do nothing, we will be overrun!',
	$9395210: 'We can not handle this force with our limited resource, Funke. This is too much!',
	$9395230: 'The Americans are crossing to the North, we WILL be overrun!',
	$9395240: 'WHAT do we DO Hauptmann! We need leadership! Now!',
	$9395250: 'The Americans? . . .they arrived so quickly.',
	$9395260: 'Man the defenses! Every soldier to his post!',
	$9395261: '. . . Bormann, ready my staff car!',
	$9395270: 'Hold them back! Believe in the strength of your German guns!',
	$9395280: 'Give me time to think! Keep the bridgeways secured!',
	$9395290: 'What do you think you should do? Push them back!',
	$9395300: 'Shoot them! Kill them! Do not fail me!',
	$9395301: 'Reinforcements have arrived! We are saved!',
	$9395330: 'We must take back all ground lost, at ANY cost!',
	$9395331: 'They are attacking the church!',
	$9395340: 'I do not have any orders, just kill them! Kill the Americans!',
	$9395341: 'The Americans, where are they going?',
	$9395342: 'It appears the Americans are easing off.',
	$9395350: 'Hauptmann Funke! We have radio contact with High Command!',
	$9395360: 'They wish to speak to you to relay orders!',
	$9395370: 'It is about time! We are getting out of here.',
	$9395380: 'Please repeat! The signal is very weak.',
	$9395390:
		'Your orders are as follows: You must hold Trun until the entire 7th army has evacuated the pocket.',
	$9395400: 'No, we’re still not hearing you. Here, let me try something.',
	$9395410: 'These are your orders!',
	$9395420: 'Gentlemen, I suggest that we leave immediately.',
	$9395430: 'Leave? As long as Germans are fighting their way to Trun, we must keep the door open!',
	$9395440:
		'Well then Hess, congratulations. You are hereby promoted OBERLEUTNANT effective immediately. You can stay if you want to.',
	$9395450:
		'The 7th has not made it to the town. If you go now, you are disobeying a direct order from High Command.',
	$9395460: 'As far as high command knows, that order never made it to Trun.',
	$9395470:
		'Anyone that doesn’t want to die here is free to join me. Otherwise, good luck gentlemen.',
	$9399001: 'Another day draws to a close and Trun is still held.',
	$9399002: 'The Allies have crushed the Falaise Pocket too soon.',
	$9399504: 'Hold Garrisons',
	$9399505: 'Maintain control over the Axis garrisons. Do not let them fall to the Americans.',
	$9399506: 'Garrisons Held',
	$9399507: 'Hold All Territory',
	$9399508:
		'Do not let the Allies claim any of the Trun territory.  Retake any lost territory before the day ends.',
