	$9399632: 'Recapture Victory Point',
	$9399633: 'Destroy Enemy Tank',
	$9399634: 'Eliminate Enemy Squad',
	$9399635: 'Build Tank Traps',
	$9399636: 'Build Barbed Wire',
	$9399637: 'Bury Landmines',
	$9399638: 'Build Sandbags',
	$9399639: 'Defend Position',
	$9400000: 'Mein Gott.  The Americans knew exactly where they would be.  Damn High Command!',
	$9400010: 'All of this is starting to feel like one giant suicide mission.',
	$9400020: 'Our Panzers are destroyed - what hope do we possibly have?',
	$9400030: "We've stayed longer than anyone could expect!",
	$9400040:
		'Expected by whom? By cowards! By idiots!  I will not leave my fellow countrymen behind to be swallowed up by the Americans.',
	$9400050: 'WE will not leave them behind.',
	$9400060: "But without communication from High Command, we won't know when to...",
	$9400070: 'Fuck High Command! Our last orders were to stay. So we stay.',
	$9400090: 'Then what will you have us do?!',
	$9400110:
		'In mere moments, our brothers will be streaming in from the North, hopefully with some remnants of the Oberst’s Panzers.',
	$9400120:
		'If we let the Allies take positions across the river, our men will run into a hail of bullets.',
	$9400121: 'We need to keep the Allies contained.',
	$9400122: 'Set up defenses along the river here, here and here.',
	$9400125: 'Members of the 7th army have arrived!',
	$9400126: 'Good.  We must keep the Allies out of their way, and keep the evacuation route open!',
	$9400127: 'Oberleutnant! The Canadians are trying to cross the river!',
	$9400128: 'We cannot let that happen! All men to the river! Push them back!',
	$9400129: 'This cannot end here!',
	$9400130: 'Good job, men. The Canadians have retreated back across the river.',
	$9400131: 'Shore up the river crossing points.',
	$9400132: 'Build tank traps, barbed wire; plug them up!',
	$9400133: 'Where are the traps? We need them down now!',
	$9400134: 'Good job, men. That should keep those dogs back for now. Now, defend the line!',
	$9400135: 'The bridge! The Americans are trying to take the bridge!',
	$9400136: 'Force them back!',
	$9400137: 'We did it! We pushed them back!',
	$9400138: "It's not time to celebrate. The Americans won't give up that easily.",
	$9400139: "Whatever their plans, we won't make it easy for them. Destroy the bridge!",
	$9400140: "Can you hear that? American tanks! They're trying to cut us off!",
	$9400141: 'We must keep the church square!',
	$9400142: 'Ober! The Canadians are back with more troops!',
	$9400143: 'The 7th is almost through! Everyone! Push them back! This is it!',
	$9400144: "Good job, men!  We're almost through!",
	$9400145: 'Sir! That was the last of the 7th! We must leave before they crush us!',
	$9400146: 'I know!',
	$9400147: "I can't leave anyone behind!",
	$9400148: "We've done our duty! We can go!",
	$9400149: 'Ruhe in Frieden.',
	$9400150: 'Rest in peace brothers.',
	$9400180: 'The Americans are trying to repair the bridge!',
	$9400300: 'Sir! We should leave now! The Americans have taken over!',
	$9400310: 'We must leave! Now!',
	$9400360: "Trun has fallen! I don't want to die here!",
	$9400450:
		'When the pocket collapsed, the corridor that led my German brothers to safety became an alleyway of death.',
	$9400451: 'Ten thousand died. Forty thousand loyal German troops were captured.',
	$9400452: 'But because of the bravery at Trun, many more escaped.',
	$9400453: 'My Gruppe did not contain heroes, nor martyrs.',
	$9400454:
		'We stayed in Trun, and fought because we wouldn’t have been able to live with the alternative:',
	$9400460: 'sleepless nights filled with the memories of those we had left behind.',
	$9400470:
		'I spared my men that, even if they hated me for it . . . because at least we did something.',
	$9400480: 'At least we tried.',
	$9400490: 'May God have mercy on those who ran.',
	$9404001: 'Say a prayer for those left behind.',
	$9404002: 'LXXXVI Corps has failed to support the evacuation.',
	$9404504: 'Reclaim Garrisons',
	$9404505:
		'Take back all the territory and garrisons in Trun.  The garrisons grant invaluable resources.',
	$9404506: 'Garrisons Reclaimed!',
	$9404507: 'Stop the Canadian Attack',
	$9404508:
		'The Canadians are attempting to ford the river! Push them back from the evacuating forces!',
	$9404509: 'Canadians Pushed Back',
	$9404510: 'Defend the Evacuation',
	$9404511:
		'The 7th Army is using the road to escape.  Keep the Allies at bay and the road to safety open.',
	$9404512: 'Evacuation Complete',
	$9404513: 'Ensure all Evacuees Exit',
	$9404514:
		'Do not give up, hold the crossroads open until the last of the evacuees arrive in town.',
	$9404515: 'All Evacuees Rescued',
	$9404516: 'Defend Trun',
	$9404517: 'Control the town garrisons, build defenses, and hold off the Allied advance.',
	$9404518: 'Evacuation Complete',
	$9404519: 'Evacuate From Trun',
	$9404520: "It's time for the 346th Infantry Division to evacuate Trun.",
	$9404521: 'Build Tank Traps',
	$9404522: 'Build enough Tank Traps to close off the gap in the river.',
	$9404523: 'Push Back the Americans',
	$9404524:
		'The Americans are attempting to cross the river. Prevent them from capturing the Victory Point.',
	$9404525: 'Destroy the Bridge',
	$9404526: 'Use Goliaths, artillery, or focused fire to destroy the bridge.',
	$9404527: 'Intercept American Panzers',
	$9404528: 'American panzers are pushing across the river to the South.  Stop them.',
	$9404529: 'Prevent the American panzer company from flanking the evacuation route.',
	$9404600: 'Squad Recruited',
	$9404601: 'Raise the Flag',
	$9404602: 'Axis Garrison',
	$9404603: 'Defend the Territory',
	$9404604: 'Denied: Popcap Full',
	$9404605: 'Point Captured',
