	$9430000: 'We are OUT OF TIME. Fourth Infantry needs this road.',
	$9430010:
		'First and Second platoon will make the first charge on Cauquigny, followed by the Third and Fourth.',
	$9430020: 'He. . .he’s kidding right? He can’t send anyone out there!',
	$9430030: 'Do NOT stop running. Just follow the man in front and KEEP MOVING.',
	$9430040: 'My God, they’re bein’ ripped apart!',
	$9430050: 'MOVE! MOVE! GET UP! GET UP!',
	$9430060: 'Follow me and DON’T STOP RUNNING!!',
	$9430070: 'This is crazy!',
	$9430080: 'Was it crazy to run straight into the German defense?',
	$9430085: "Probably, but I wasn't thinking about that.",
	$9430090: 'One of us had to be the first to make it across. It had to be me.',
	$9430100: 'He made it!',
	$9430110: 'He made it! He actually made it!',
	$9430120: 'We gotta get over there! WE GOTTA GET OVER THERE! CHARGE!',
	$9430130: 'We can do this! We can do this!',
	$9430140: "I can't believe I'm putting my shit on the line for this fucking road!",
	$9430160: 'Just get me to the other side!',
	$9430190: "If I'm going to die, it's going to be running at the Germans, not away from em!",
	$9430210: "Killed my buddies, now I'm gonna kill krauts!",
	$9430220: "Let's go!",
	$9430250: 'Get over there! Get over there!',
	$9430270: "Run! Run! Don't stop!",
	$9430280: "If we stop here we're dead!",
	$9430310: 'Sgt. Craft, that was incredible.',
	$9430320: "I can't believe you made it sir.",
	$9430340:
		"Christ sarge, you pull off a few more stunts like that and you'll make us all look like shmucks!",
	$9430350: 'Good to see you in one piece!',
	$9430360: "I didn't think I would see YOU again.",
	$9430370: "We’ve taken Cauquigny. Good job men! Now, let's bring the fight to them.",
	$9430380: 'The Germans are retreating here ... to Grey Castle.',
	$9430382: "They're setting up anti-tank defenses to cover their retreat.",
	$9430384: 'Our first objective, is to clear this road of AT for the armored cav.',
	$9430390: 'Our second, is to neutralize the supporting artillery.',
	$9430400: 'Once destroyed, double back and assault Grey Castle in full force.',
	$9430410: 'Let’s end this. Move out.',
	$9430430: 'That was an ace shot sir!',
	$9430440: "Thank God you're on our side Craft!",
	$9430450: 'Wild, Craft!  That was wild!',
	$9430460: 'Thank god they’re here! Does that mean we get to go home now?',
	$9430470: 'We’re soldiers, private. We ARE home.',
	$9430480:
		"A soldier once told me that you'll know when you find yourself in a good place to die.",
	$9430490:
		"It won't feel like a sacrifice, it will feel like an opportunity. This moment, will be obvious, and clear.",
	$9430500: 'The decision will be simple.',
	$9430510: 'The decision, will be made for you.',
	$9430550: 'When hundreds of lives are at stake one doesn’t seem so significant.',
	$9430560: 'But sometimes, one can make all the difference.',
	$9430570: 'We have to get past those MG nests! Take them out!',
	$9430580: 'Lay some fire on those nests now!',
	$9430590: 'Mg nests destroyed, move forward on Cauquigny!',
	$9430600: "Let's go men! Moving forward!",
	$9430610: 'Take out those AT guns! We have to open the road!',
	$9430620: 'All AT are destroyed; the road should be clear now.',
	$9430630: "Now we'll get some support!",
	$9430640: 'We need to take out that artillery!',
	$9430650: 'God knows what those guns are doing to the boys on the beach.',
	$9430660: "Good job men, keep your gear on, we're not done yet.",
	$9430662: 'It is time to clear out Grey Castle.',
	$9430664: 'This is it men, one last push.',
	$9430670: "That's the tank that ran over Wilson.",
